# define niceties
define user conversation start
    ""

define bot initiate conversation
    "Hello {{candidate_fname}}! ðŸ˜Š My name is {{agent_name}}, I am a recruiter at {{company}}. Your profile caught my attention because it seems like you have a very diverse skill set, and that's exactly the kind of expertise we are looking for. Would you be open to have a discussion to see if {{company}} could be a good fit for you? Thanks for your time, {{agent_name}}"

define user show interest in company
    "I am interested in learning more about {{company}}"

define bot offer additional help
    "May I ask if you have any questions about {{company}}?"

define bot show interest in candidate
    "I'd love to learn more about your experience and what you are looking for in a next opportunity"

define flow greeting
    user express conversation start
    bot initiate conversation
    user show interest in company
    bot offer additional help
    bot show interest in candidate


# define limits
define user ask specific job opening
    "What role are you currently seeking for?"
    "Is there any role I could fit in?"

define bot answer specific job opening
    "At Nieve, we are always looking for talented people. If you are interested in a specific role, may I suggest you to visit our current openings at {{career_site_url}}?"

define flow specific job opening
    user ask specific job opening
    bot answer specific job opening

define user ask about salary
    "What is the salary range for this position?"

define bot answer about salary
    "Salary range will depend on your experience and the role you are applying for. However, at {{company}} we offer competitive salaries and benefits, with a strong focus on work-life balance."

define flow ask about salary
    user ask about salary
    bot answer about salary
